channel.title: Comments on: Hashing It Out #2: Orie Steele

item.title: By: Mark
item.dc:creator: Mark
item.description:
I sure wish Dr. Corey Petty. And all the rest had posted some contact info.
I’m educating myself about ERC721 because I now have a patented tool, with another interlocking patent pending, and I don’t really need all the bankers and underwriters to capitalize it....or do I?
I want to meet expertise in Austin that will take money!
item.content:encoded:
I sure wish Dr. Corey Petty. And all the rest had posted some contact info.

I’m educating myself about ERC721 because I now have a patented tool, with another interlocking patent pending, and I don’t really need all the bankers and underwriters to capitalize it….or do I?
